scheduled_maintenances.name: Scheduled Maintenance for the US & EU Regions - November 10th from 06:00 UTC to 09:00 UTC

incident_updates.body:
We intend to perform maintenance on Sunday, November 10th from 06:00 UTC to 09:00 UTC (or Saturday, November 9th from 22:00 PST to 01:00 PST). Customers in the US & EU regions can expect a short service interruption at some point during this timeframe which may include anomalies for New Relic as described below:
- inability to render the New Relic UI
- inability to communicate with various APIs
- inability to complete a new user sign up

Please note, we do not anticipate impact to data ingest or alert notifications. All further updates will be posted here on our status page.
